## Files moved away from MIT

This project was previously MIT-licensed. The MIT license still applies to all
commits up to and including the one preceding the relicense commit — historical
versions of files in the git history are unaffected. From the relicense commit
forward, everything is dual-licensed as described above.

For attribution and contact, write to
[ceo@uitbreiden.com](mailto:ceo@uitbreiden.com) or open an issue at
https://github.com/UitbreidenOS/UitKit.
